                <li title="One-off rebuild: fetches full 5-year price history from Yahoo for all Watchlist symbols. Use after adding new watchlist entries or rebuilding the History table from scratch."><a href="#" @onclick="updates.UpdateWatchlistHistoryAsync" @onclick:preventDefault="true">Rebuild Watchlist History</a></li>
